                    (source of the text reproduced here). <emph>Document summaries</emph>: Di Meo
                    1795-1819, III, p. 95; Cappelletti 1845, p. 45; Poupardin 1907, Catalogue, I, n.
                    2 A p. 66 (v. Smidt 1910 pp. 111-112); Voigt 1902, 3, p. 59; RIM, 391.</p>
            </div>
